title: Javascript for Beginners in Hindi | Learn Javascript in 100 minutes | Great Learning
description: Watch this tutorial on JavaScript For Beginners in Hindi! JavaScript, also simply known as JS, is a high-level and multi-paradigm programming language. JavaScript is famously used for web-development purposes and is a text-oriented language following prototype-based object-orientation along with dynamic typing. Along with being considered to be one of the easier programming languages, it is extremely popular as web-development is considered to an extremely sought-after career option in today‚Äôs digital world.Great Learning brings you this tutorial on JavaScript For Beginners in Hindi to help you understand everything you need to know about this topic and getting started on the journey to learn about it well. This video starts off with an introduction to JavaScript, its history, tools and JS Hello World, followed by understanding the comments, variables and datatypes of JavaScript. Then we look at type coercion, JavaScript properties and operators. Finally, we look at conditional statements, loops and arrays in JS! This video teaches JavaScript and its key functions and concepts with a variety of demonstrations & examples to help you get started on the right foot
